Interface MultiPartShapeM

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
MultiPatchShp, PolygonMShp, PolygonZShp, PolylineMShp, PolylineZShp
public interface MultiPartShapeM
extends MultiPartShape

This class declares the methods that are common to all multipart Shapes with Measures. The starting index for both points and parts is 0.
